name: Sunlight Triangles
description:
Brighten your outfit with these unique yellow, orange and red feather earrings! Just looking at this set of earrings makes me smile!

Consisting of 4 feathers with shades of yellow, orange and red. Antique brass chain gives the earrings a natural feel and sparkle with a bit of swarovski.

name: Tiger Stripes Pheasant Feather Earrings
description:
This wonderful combination of white pheasant and golden pheasant plumage creates a stunning set of earrings. The layering effect creates a beautiful tiger stripe pattern! They are a real head turner and ideal with black, white or orange outfits.

These long earrings hang nicely from the ear. They consist of 3 pheasant feathers per earring wrapped in orange wire and complimented by a bicone swarovski crystal. They hang from sterling silver earwires.

Approximately 100mm L x 30mm W

There are many breeds of Pheasants. These earrings consist of feathers from the golden pheasant and Lady Amherst (white). Pheasants don’t fly they are ground dwellers and although brightly coloured they camouflage well when walking in grasses.

Thanks for looking!

FREE SHIPPING UNTIL APRIL 30

name: Black Peacock Feather Earrings
description:
Elegance at its best. This set of black peacock feather earrings brings style and class to any outfit. They sit wonderfully on the neckline and don’t tickle. 

Bringing a twist to traditional peacock feather eye earrings, this set is complimented black and gold speckled Indian glass beads and hung from gold plated earwires. 

Gold splashes can be found throughout the feathers as well as hints of deep purple. They are simply stunning feathers.

Approximately 100mm L x 40mm W

FREE SHIPPING UNTIL APRIL 30

name: Tropical Feather Earrings
description:
I always wanted to combine orange and blue and now I have!

A brand new addition to my feather earring range. This colour combination is sure to turn heads and brighten your black or colourful outfits. They sit nicely on the jaw line and are lightweight. 

Consisting of dark blue, bright blue, orange, jewel pheasant plumage (iridescent green) and spotted natural guinea feathers. I have also added a fire (orange, red) swarovski crystal to finish the earrings and highlight the orange of the earrings. 

Ear wires are made from antique brass to match the feathers. These can be changed to sterling silver for sensitive ears, just let me know on purchase.

Handmade and unique from Australia. Feathers are like fingerprints so you can make an individual statement.

85mm L x 30mm W.

FREE SHIPPING
